title: Repository missing project-level CLAUDE.md for contributor onboarding

evidence.snippet: No CLAUDE.md found at project root /Users/tsk/multi-cli-orchestrator/

recommendation: Add a project-level CLAUDE.md documenting build commands, architecture overview, and contribution conventions to reduce onboarding friction.

title: Missing CODEOWNERS reduces maintainability of review ownership

evidence.snippet: No CODEOWNERS file is defined at the repository root to document ownership boundaries.

recommendation: Add a root-level CODEOWNERS file mapping key paths to responsible maintainers to improve long-term maintainability and review routing.

title: Magic String for Configuration Key
recommendation: Replace the magic string 'config' with a named constant to improve readability and reduce the risk of typos.

title: 仓库上下文为空导致可维护性基线不足
recommendation: 补充最小可维护性基线：添加 `README`（项目用途与运行方式）、基础代码结构说明，以及统一的格式化/静态检查配置（如 `editorconfig`、lint/format 脚本），以降低后续协作与审查成本。

title: Magic number in configuration without named constant

evidence.snippet: timeout or parallelism value used directly without const

recommendation: Extract magic numbers to named constants with descriptive names for better code maintainability
